Oneohtrix Point Never

              Russian Mind
            
              (NO FUN / Software Recording Co.)
label: NO FUN / Software Recording Co.
description:
Oneohtrix Point Never's 'Russian Mind' is centred around the theme of a Russian cosmonaut past his prime, composing the score to a film from his hospital bed in a room on the east wing of an orbiting infirmary, facing a window overlooking a grove of holographic birch trees.
